query:
SELECT LOWER(name) as "name!", MAX(version) as "latest_version?",
               COUNT(DISTINCT version)::bigint as "version_count!",
               SUM(size_bytes)::bigint as "total_size?"
        FROM artifacts
        WHERE repository_id = $1
          AND is_deleted = false
          AND LOWER(name) LIKE $2
        GROUP BY LOWER(name)
        ORDER BY LOWER(name)
        LIMIT $3 OFFSET $4
